picche <colour id="7" />♠ <colour id="65535" />e fiori <colour id="7" />♣<colour id="65535" />?
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Io ne prenderò una.<delay20 /> A questo punto<delay frames="13" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />tu dovrai indovinarne il colore!<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Se indovini, ti regalerò <delay frames="13" /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="50" b="17" arg="0x12 0xcd00 0xc 0x69 0x6c 0x20 0x6d 0x69 0x6f 0xc 0x6c 0x61 0x20 0x6d 0x69 0x61 0x0" />
<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />!<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Facilissimo, no?
<anim id="NpcShuffle" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Bene!<delay20 /> Allora iniziamo<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Ecco fatto! Ho pescato una carta.
Ora dimmi<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Il seme è <colour id="6" />rosso<colour id="65535" /> <delay frames="13" />come le mie scarpe
con i tacchi alti <delay frames="40" /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />o <colour id="7" />nero<colour id="65535" /> come il mio
vestito da sera preferito?</message>
	<message label="201_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><colour id="6" />Rosso<colour id="65535" />!</message>
	<message label="201_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><colour id="7" />Nero<colour id="65535" />!</message>
